This is a fork of the original nano-vLLM project by Xingkai Yu.
The original project can be found at: https://github.com/GeeeekExplorer/nano-vllm

Modifications made in this fork:
- Added Runpod serverless deployment support
- OpenAI-compatible API wrapper
- Production deployment configuration
- Docker containerization for Runpod Hub

